text: In #Pakistan, from 3rd Jan '20 to 2nd April '21, there have been  672,931 confirmed cases of #COVID19 with 14,530 deaths. As of 25th Mar '21, a total of 659,467 #vaccine doses administered which comes out to be 0.3 per 100 population. One of the lowest in the world. #WHO https://t.co/Vp8kcg1zkt
